data.meta_description: Home - North Kansas City School District
data.text:
An award-winning school district serving more than 21,500 learners in Kansas City's Northland.

Preparing our students for success beyond graduation

Ready to enroll? Take the next step with online registration for new students, open now.

With 110 years of serving our community, NKC Schools honors tradition with forward-thinking vision.

Ready to enroll? Take the next step this summer with online registration for new students, open now.

North Kansas City Schools serves more than 21,500 learners as the second-largest and one of the most diverse school districts in Missouri.
